                            <comment id="468052" author="JIRAUSER19288" created="Tue, 19 Aug 2025 15:13:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This issue was resolved in the context of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18357&quot; title=&quot;Support multiple filesets per nodemap&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-18357&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-18357&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Previously, &lt;tt&gt;lctl nodemap_set_fileset&lt;/tt&gt; was only a local operation and not persistent. This was fixed and further deprecated in favor of the commands &lt;tt&gt;lctl nodemap_fileset_add&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;lctl nodemap_fileset_del&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
